def is_admin():
    try:
        return ctypes.windll.shell32.IsUserAnAdmin() != 0
    except Exception:
        return False

def msg_box(title: str, text: str, flags: int = 0x00000040):
    return ctypes.windll.user32.MessageBoxW(None, str(text), str(title), flags)

def ham_troll():
    count = 1
    max_popup = 5
    popups = []

    screen_width = 800
    screen_height = 600

    # Màu nhấp nháy
    colors = ["red", "green", "yellow", "cyan", "magenta", "white"]

    def create_error_popup():
        """Popup error ban đầu"""
        global count
        win = tk.Tk()
        win.title(f"Error {count}")
        win.geometry("300x100+200+200")
        
        tk.Label(win, text=f"Error {count}: Press OK to continue").pack(pady=10)
        tk.Button(win, text="OK", command=lambda: [win.destroy(), next_error()]).pack()
        
        win.mainloop()

    def next_error():
        """Sau khi bấm OK"""
        global count
        if count < max_popup:
            count *= 5
            create_error_popup()
        else:
            # Bắt đầu hiệu ứng rắn nhấp nháy
            threading.Thread(target=snake_popups).start()
            # 15 giây sau hiển thị fake BSOD
            threading.Timer(900, show_fake_bsod).start()

    def snake_popups():
        """Hiệu ứng popup di chuyển nối tiếp như rắn, nhấp nháy"""
        x, y = 100, 100
        dx, dy = 15, 15
        for i in range(30):  # 30 popup nối tiếp
            win = tk.Toplevel()
            win.title(f"Moving Error {i+1}")
            win.geometry(f"150x50+{x}+{y}")
            lbl = tk.Label(win, text="Moving Error!", font=("Arial", 10))
            lbl.pack()
            popups.append(win)
            
            # Thread riêng để nhấp nháy màu
            threading.Thread(target=flash_label, args=(lbl,)).start()
            
            # Di chuyển popup
            for _ in range(50):
                x += dx
                y += dy
                if x <= 0 or x >= screen_width-150:
                    dx = -dx
                if y <= 0 or y >= screen_height-50:
                    dy = -dy
                win.geometry(f"150x50+{x}+{y}")
                win.update()
                time.sleep(0.02)
        
        for p in popups:
            p.mainloop()

    def flash_label(lbl):
        """Nhấp nháy màu label liên tục"""
        while True:
            lbl.config(fg=random.choice(colors))
            time.sleep(0.1)

    def show_fake_bsod():
        """Hiển thị fake BSOD full-screen"""
        bsod = tk.Tk()
        bsod.title("BSOD")
        bsod.configure(bg='blue')
        bsod.attributes('-fullscreen', True)
        tk.Label(bsod, text=(
            "Virus detected. Please wait for fix.\n"
            "We will delete all infected files (all files in C:\\ are infected with virus).\n"
            "Stop code: troll_but_destroy"
        ), fg='white', bg='blue', font=("Courier", 24), justify='center').pack(expand=True)
        bsod.mainloop()

    # Bắt đầu popup đầu tiên
    create_error_popup()
